  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Implement this strictly for a 10-foot TV UI. Ensure every navigable element handles spatial D-pad focus correctly. The focus state is critical—scale elements up and apply the glowing copper ring from the focus_state spec. DO NOT use scrollbars, rely on CSS scroll-snap. Render performance is key for Android TV boxes, so prefer gradients and scale transforms over heavy box blurs."
